# ============================================================================
# src/algebra/SOURCES -- algebra source manifest
# ============================================================================
#
# This file lists all algebra source files that are part of the OpenAxiom
# build.  One basename per line (without path or extension).  For each
# entry, the build system looks for <name>.spad.pamphlet first, then
# <name>.spad.  Pamphlets are extracted via `hammer --tangle`; plain .spad
# files are used directly.
#
# ADDING A NEW FILE
# -----------------
# To add a new algebra source:
#   1. Create  foo.spad.pamphlet  or  foo.spad  in this directory.
#   2. Add "foo" to this file (anywhere; alphabetical order preferred).
#   3. Re-run cmake.  The scanner will discover all constructors in the
#      new file and assign any not in an explicit layer to the catch-all
#      layer.
#
# The build system will warn at configure time if a .spad.pamphlet or
# .spad file exists in this directory but is not listed here.
#
# REMOVING A FILE
# ---------------
# Delete the entry from this file and remove the source file.
#
# 322 entries (current pamphlet count).
# ============================================================================

